      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Operation Khezu",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "\u003CPL\u003E, you\u0027ve\r\nreceived orders from The Kingdom\r\nto commence an investigation.\r\nIt must be thorough, so enlist allies\r\nto aid you. I wish you and your\r\nchosen comrades the best of luck.\r\nDo not let your guard down.",
        "Target": "Hunt a Khezu",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Op\u00E9ration Khezu",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "\u003CPL\u003E, nous avons\r\nre\u00E7u des ordres du Royaume\r\nconcernant une t\u00E2che. Tu n\u0027as\r\npas le droit \u00E0 l\u0027erreur, donc\r\nrecrute des alli\u00E9s. Je vous\r\nsouhaite \u00E0 tous bonne chance,\r\net faites attention !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Khezu",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Operazione Khezu",
        "Client": "Dama Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Salve, \u003CPL\u003E, hai\r\nricevuto ordini dal regno di\r\navviare un\u0027indagine. Dovr\u00E0\r\nessere approfondita, dunque\r\narruola alleati al tuo fianco.\r\nAuguro buona fortuna a te e ai\r\ntuoi colleghi. State all\u0027erta.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Khezu",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Operation Khezu",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "\u003CPL\u003E, das K\u00F6nigreich\r\nbefiehlt dir, eine Unter-\r\nsuchung einzuleiten. Suche dir\r\nhierf\u00FCr die Unterst\u00FCtzung von\r\nVerb\u00FCndeten. Ich w\u00FCnsche dir\r\nund den von dir gew\u00E4hlten Kame-\r\nraden viel Gl\u00FCck. Sei wachsam!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Khezu.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Operaci\u00F3n Khezu",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "El reino te ha dado \u00F3rdenes de\r\nemprender una investigaci\u00F3n,\r\n\u003CPL\u003E.\r\nLa misi\u00F3n es compleja, por lo\r\nque debes rodearte de aliados.\r\nOs deseo buena suerte a ti y a\r\ntus camaradas. Estad alerta.",
        "Target": "Caza un Khezu",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041E\u043F\u0435\u0440\u0430\u0446\u0438\u044F \u0022\u041A\u0435\u0437\u0443\u0022",
        "Client": "\u0420\u044B\u0446\u0430\u0440\u044C \u0424\u0438\u043E\u0440\u0430\u0439\u043D\u0430",
        "Description": "\u003CPL\u003E, \u041A\u043E\u0440\u043E\u043B\u0435\u0432\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043E\r\n\u043F\u0440\u0438\u043A\u0430\u0437\u044B\u0432\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0430\u043C \u043D\u0430\u0447\u0430\u0442\u044C\r\n\u0440\u0430\u0441\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u043E\u0432\u0430\u043D\u0438\u0435. \u041E\u043D\u043E \u0434\u043E\u043B\u0436\u043D\u043E \u0431\u044B\u0442\u044C\r\n\u0432\u0441\u0435\u0441\u0442\u043E\u0440\u043E\u043D\u043D\u0438\u043C, \u043F\u043E\u044D\u0442\u043E\u043C\u0443 \u0432\u0430\u043C\r\n\u043F\u043E\u043D\u0430\u0434\u043E\u0431\u0438\u0442\u0441\u044F \u043F\u043E\u043C\u043E\u0449\u044C. \u0416\u0435\u043B\u0430\u044E\r\n\u0443\u0434\u0430\u0447\u0438 \u0432\u0430\u043C \u0438 \u0432\u0430\u0448\u0438\u043C \u0441\u043E\u0440\u0430\u0442\u043D\u0438\u043A\u0430\u043C.\r\n\u041D\u0435 \u0442\u0435\u0440\u044F\u0439\u0442\u0435 \u0431\u0434\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043B\u044C\u043D\u043E\u0441\u0442\u0438.",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u041A\u0435\u0437\u0443",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
